1
00:00:06,340 --> 00:00:07,260
I understand.

2
00:00:07,740 --> 00:00:09,260
I'll make it happen.

3
00:00:09,540 --> 00:00:10,940
Think carefully.

4
00:00:11,540 --> 00:00:13,660
Using forbidden arts
to revive your master

5
00:00:13,900 --> 00:00:16,540
will make you an enemy
of the whole immortal realm.

6
00:00:17,100 --> 00:00:18,300
Even so,

7
00:00:18,700 --> 00:00:19,740
would you still do it?

8
00:00:19,940 --> 00:00:21,140
Forget the immortal realm.

9
00:00:22,580 --> 00:00:24,780
I wouldn't hesitate
even if it meant opposing

10
00:00:25,460 --> 00:00:26,740
all the Three Realms.

11
00:00:26,900 --> 00:00:27,700
Very well.

12
00:00:30,660 --> 00:00:31,460
What's this?

13
00:00:31,980 --> 00:00:33,860
This is our Shadow Clan's
divine artifact,

14
00:00:34,300 --> 00:00:35,460
the Shadow Moon Pendant.

15
00:00:37,460 --> 00:00:38,420
Wear it,

16
00:00:38,860 --> 00:00:40,940
and it will conceal
the fiendish aura on you.

17
00:00:41,460 --> 00:00:42,620
So the Immortals

18
00:00:43,140 --> 00:00:44,340
won't be able to find you.

19
00:00:52,070 --> 00:00:54,720
[Immortal Beyond Dust]
[Episode 14]

20
00:00:59,540 --> 00:01:00,620
Let's go home.

21
00:01:19,620 --> 00:01:20,620
Get up by yourself.

22
00:01:27,300 --> 00:01:28,980
Master likes to keep things clean.

23
00:01:29,380 --> 00:01:30,020
Looks like

24
00:01:30,460 --> 00:01:31,860
I need to buy her some new clothes.

25
00:01:32,740 --> 00:01:33,140
Come on.

26
00:01:34,660 --> 00:01:35,740
I'll take you to the mortal realm.

27
00:01:38,660 --> 00:01:39,460
Mortal realm?

28
00:01:41,100 --> 00:01:42,140
Do they have good food there?

29
00:01:57,060 --> 00:01:58,620
The mortal realm is fun.

30
00:02:09,900 --> 00:02:11,180
Miss, you haven't paid yet.

31
00:02:16,660 --> 00:02:18,940
In the mortal realm, you need money

32
00:02:19,300 --> 00:02:20,460
to buy anything.

33
00:02:21,060 --> 00:02:21,860
Money.

34
00:02:24,260 --> 00:02:24,700
Here.

35
00:02:25,540 --> 00:02:26,060
Thank you.

36
00:02:28,460 --> 00:02:29,260
Eat.

37
00:02:34,100 --> 00:02:35,540
Come take a look!

38
00:02:38,460 --> 00:02:39,740
Miss, have a look.

39
00:02:40,060 --> 00:02:41,460
See how exquisite this mask is.

40
00:02:48,260 --> 00:02:49,300
Want some tanghulu?

41
00:02:50,980 --> 00:02:51,260
Here.

42
00:02:51,660 --> 00:02:52,780
Tanghulu. Take it.

43
00:02:54,060 --> 00:02:55,580
Tanghulu!

44
00:02:57,140 --> 00:02:57,740
Money.

45
00:02:58,820 --> 00:02:59,340
I'll take one.

46
00:03:05,340 --> 00:03:05,780
Alright.

47
00:03:06,060 --> 00:03:07,220
Thank you. Here.

48
00:03:07,580 --> 00:03:08,140
Take it.

49
00:03:09,700 --> 00:03:10,940
Tanghulu!

50
00:03:16,180 --> 00:03:16,620
Sweet!

51
00:03:30,260 --> 00:03:31,580
Are you here to check out the clothes?

52
00:03:32,140 --> 00:03:33,540
Miss, look over here.

53
00:03:35,020 --> 00:03:36,860
Miss, you're breathtakingly beautiful.

54
00:03:36,860 --> 00:03:38,060
This dress would surely suit you.

55
00:03:38,060 --> 00:03:38,820
Try it on.

56
00:03:40,380 --> 00:03:41,340
Come try it.

57
00:03:44,860 --> 00:03:45,900
Go ahead and try it.

58
00:03:46,740 --> 00:03:48,220
Alright. Miss, right this way.

59
00:04:01,900 --> 00:04:03,060
Let her try this set as well.

60
00:04:17,020 --> 00:04:17,700
Kites!

61
00:04:18,020 --> 00:04:18,940
Look at the kites!

62
00:04:41,220 --> 00:04:41,660
The mortal realm

63
00:04:42,060 --> 00:04:42,620
is fun.

64
00:04:43,100 --> 00:04:43,740
I want to go again.

65
00:04:44,620 --> 00:04:45,820
Better not.

66
00:04:46,860 --> 00:04:47,460
Why?

67
00:04:47,780 --> 00:04:48,300
Go.

68
00:04:52,140 --> 00:04:53,820
If you behave,

69
00:04:54,860 --> 00:04:56,140
I might consider it.

70
00:04:59,260 --> 00:05:00,460
First, put these things away properly.

71
00:05:00,660 --> 00:05:01,220
Okay.

72
00:05:16,660 --> 00:05:17,740
If you're hungry,

73
00:05:18,260 --> 00:05:19,860
eat your fill before starting work.

74
00:05:24,860 --> 00:05:25,660
Come on.

75
00:05:26,060 --> 00:05:26,860
I'll teach you.

76
00:05:33,660 --> 00:05:34,260
Scriptures

77
00:05:35,140 --> 00:05:35,940
go here.

78
00:05:48,500 --> 00:05:50,140
The brush goes on the rack.

79
00:05:53,460 --> 00:05:55,100
The paperweight goes on the far right.

80
00:05:57,700 --> 00:05:58,740
A bit more to the right.

81
00:06:05,100 --> 00:06:06,060
Fold the sleeves first.

82
00:06:11,660 --> 00:06:12,620
Then fold the garment.

83
00:06:13,140 --> 00:06:13,660
Fold it neatly.

84
00:06:18,020 --> 00:06:18,660
Make sure

85
00:06:19,180 --> 00:06:20,300
the flowers match in color.

86
00:06:21,740 --> 00:06:22,460
Give it a try.

87
00:06:46,220 --> 00:06:47,100
These two characters

88
00:06:47,420 --> 00:06:48,460
are "Ruoxi".

89
00:06:49,460 --> 00:06:50,140
Ruo.

90
00:06:50,460 --> 00:06:51,340
Xi.

91
00:06:51,940 --> 00:06:53,260
When you hold the brush,

92
00:06:53,620 --> 00:06:54,660
keep the shaft straight.

93
00:06:55,940 --> 00:06:57,660
[Ruoxi]
Only by learning to read and write

94
00:06:58,740 --> 00:07:00,260
can you understand immortal texts.

95
00:07:00,820 --> 00:07:03,100
That's how you can cultivate
immortal arts.

96
00:07:03,820 --> 00:07:04,820
Immortal arts?

97
00:07:05,140 --> 00:07:06,060
Focus.

98
00:07:06,460 --> 00:07:07,860
Don't look at me. Look at the brush.

99
00:07:08,520 --> 00:07:10,640
[Ruoxi]

100
00:07:12,860 --> 00:07:13,860
When holding the brush,

101
00:07:14,660 --> 00:07:15,740
your hand mustn't shake.

102
00:07:16,260 --> 00:07:17,820
The brushstrokes must be
strong and firm.

103
00:07:18,500 --> 00:07:19,900
No weakness.

104
00:07:27,500 --> 00:07:28,620
Write it like this a hundred times.

105
00:07:29,460 --> 00:07:30,620
I'll check it later.

106
00:07:37,020 --> 00:07:38,620
A hundred times?

107
00:08:34,420 --> 00:08:35,340
Sweet.

108
00:08:48,900 --> 00:08:49,940
Bai Ruoxi!

109
00:08:55,500 --> 00:08:56,300
Stop right there!

110
00:08:58,060 --> 00:08:58,940
You little mess!

111
00:09:11,660 --> 00:09:12,180
What...

112
00:09:12,820 --> 00:09:13,620
What's wrong?

113
00:09:15,420 --> 00:09:16,700
I must not develop feelings.

114
00:09:44,340 --> 00:09:47,080
♪What is flickering?♪

115
00:09:47,300 --> 00:09:49,820
♪Shining, delicate, and bright♪

116
00:09:49,980 --> 00:09:55,820
♪Like a trace of bitterness in a smile♪

117
00:09:55,860 --> 00:09:58,700
♪What is falling?♪

118
00:09:59,140 --> 00:10:01,940
♪Clean, precise, and light♪

119
00:10:02,180 --> 00:10:07,380
♪Like enduring too many farewells♪

120
00:10:08,300 --> 00:10:09,900
♪When petals drift down♪

121
00:10:09,940 --> 00:10:11,400
♪When the rain falls all around♪

122
00:10:11,500 --> 00:10:14,100
♪I gaze into your eyes♪

123
00:10:14,260 --> 00:10:15,960
♪Beyond the dunes♪

124
00:10:16,060 --> 00:10:17,340
♪No end in sight♪

125
00:10:17,340 --> 00:10:20,340
♪I am like a mayfly♪

126
00:10:20,500 --> 00:10:21,900
♪I won't ask what the future holds♪

127
00:10:21,940 --> 00:10:23,400
♪Nor will I run away♪

128
00:10:23,420 --> 00:10:26,360
♪Through all seasons by my side♪

129
00:10:26,360 --> 00:10:31,620
♪Searching for sparks in the dust♪

130
00:10:45,940 --> 00:10:48,680
♪What is flickering?♪

131
00:10:48,900 --> 00:10:51,380
♪Shining, delicate, and bright♪

132
00:10:51,580 --> 00:10:57,380
♪Like a trace of bitterness in a smile♪

133
00:10:57,820 --> 00:11:00,620
♪What is falling?♪

134
00:11:00,740 --> 00:11:03,560
♪Clean, precise, and light♪

135
00:11:03,780 --> 00:11:08,780
♪Like enduring too many farewells♪

136
00:11:09,900 --> 00:11:11,380
♪When petals drift down♪

137
00:11:11,380 --> 00:11:12,880
♪When the rain falls all around♪

138
00:11:12,980 --> 00:11:15,540
♪I gaze into your eyes♪
